<B><FONT SIZE=6><P ALIGN="CENTER">MPEG-2</P>
<P ALIGN="CENTER">(Generic coding of moving pictures and associated audio)</P>
<HR>
</FONT><FONT SIZE=6><P>&nbsp;</P>

<UL>
<LI>Standard established in 1994</LI>
<LI>Similar to MPEG-1 decoder</LI>
<LI>Important component: Client-server interaction</LI>
<LI>Development of video profiles (attributes) that are used for different applications (user preferences)</LI>
<LI>Variable bitrates from 1.5 to 80 Mbit/s</LI></UL>

